<HEADLINE> Jacquet to Be More Cautious Against South Africa </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>

<P>
MARSEILLE, June 11 (Xinhua) -- French coach Aime Jacquet will be
more cautious in the match against South Africa which will be played
in the soccer-mad city Marseille on Friday.
</P>
<P>
After two months of working with a three-man defence and an
attacking midfield, Jacquet is set to revert to four defenders at
the back while at the same time field two defensive midfielders.
</P>
