Jacquet's revision of tactics means that full-backs Bixente
Lizarazu and Lilian Thuram will be told to refrain from their
attacking instincts.
</P>
<P>
French can expect a tough challenge from the South African team
who announced earlier that they would play a physical game against
the French team. 
