research planning and prioritization at local research center,"
the release quoted Amar Jit Sodhi, a senior management specialist
in charge of the project at the bank, as saying.
</P>
<P>
It added that farmers will communicate their needs to these
research centers, priorities will be assessed in partnership, and
locally-relevant technological research will be carried out to
address these needs. 
