drinking among the young for the rise in violent crime.
</P>
<P>
The Guardian:
</P>
<P>
-- Britain was Wednesday night held responsible for plunging
Europe's bureaucratic machine into chaos, blocking more than 260
million pounds of Europe's social budget and forcing the closure
of the European Commission's computerized payments system.
